data.description: Within walking distance of Lake Arlington this classic split-level residence boasts captivating lake views, expansive living spaces, and a lavish pool and spa. Situated on a generous one-third acre parcel adorned with mature trees and gentle slopes, this home provides a tranquil setting amidst breathtaking scenery. Four spacious bedrooms, offer privacy and comfort for diverse living arrangements. The lower level introduces a versatile bonus room, potentially a fifth bedroom or a mother-in-law suite, complete with a full kitchen. This additional space adds an extra layer of convenience and adaptability to the home. A three-car garage ensure convenient access and ample covered parking. The renowned Tiffany Park community, characterized by its established prestige, fosters a lively atmosphere with residents strolling, boating, and enjoying family activities.
